import { Box, Dialog, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const AuthForm = () => {
  return (
    <Dialog open={true}>
        <Typography variant='h4' textAlign={"center"}>
            Login
        </Typography>
        <form>
            <Box display={'flex'} justifyContent={'center'}>

            </Box>
        </form>
    </Dialog>
  )
}

export default AuthForm
